{"tid":1572182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民意逆轉撚 又贏一仗","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T11:35:14.000Z","uid":216828,"like":270,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a548e4c205fef42707ba5baa1a4f9f9c325e28","tid":1572182,"uid":216828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"係藍屍民意逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說 今日要同班藍屍親戚補返中秋節飯<br />\n行完就要走。搞到無得同勇武手足並肩作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班雨革時已經藍撚到仆街<br />\n咁於是我就想撚下佢地 突登遲到 著住黑衫 帶gear 去食 諗住引下戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知去到無人出聲 成班笑笑囗 又夾定餸畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是我就問老豆老母 班藍屍做咩事 唔撚同曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來 佢到係group 見到 火燒狗肉  同水炮車著撚左火 驚到仆街 全部笠撚曬水<br />\n  成晚咩都無屌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係多謝勇武手足嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未走嘅手足要平平安安<br />\n<br />\n我地要走嘅路仲有好遠，但我地一定會成功<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a3eeaae38d8674690f76c9133d43ab7058202e09","tid":1572182,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6ad30ae6e64b59c9d82d65791f0c7620e7a79e","tid":1572182,"uid":216828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"08bf6246c5d49fbb6cd4c2b53cb1a82871107c9f","tid":1572182,"uid":96465,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"禍必及家人"},{"pid":"bc2b251ab1e7a371f8b3e05a1363be5e1740673b","tid":1572182,"uid":216828,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"08bf6246c5d49fbb6cd4c2b53cb1a